{"tid":843261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"奶茶，咖啡，鴛鴦，你地會點揀","createTime":"2018-10-01T04:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T05:36:40.000Z","uid":203098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"10d70d18d36ab79e6ec97ccc57a782c323e6a428","tid":843261,"uid":203098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T04:28:47.000Z","msg":"以前成日叫奶茶，其實唔差，甜甜地咁<br />\n同後尾貪得意叫杯鴛鴦試下，一開始覺得苦苦地唔好飲，慢慢就上左癮，覺得嗰下苦澀先係神粹，不過好難先揾到一杯好嘅鴛鴦<br />\n<br />\n利申：淨係飲熱飲，覺得熱飲先有味<br />\n <br />\n不過灣仔金鳳嘅凍奶茶係幾好飲，唔會太凍凍到飲唔出奶茶味"},{"pid":"ab710ac89ff499ffe1e692d3578a4afc28f288ef","tid":843261,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T04:34:13.000Z","msg":"奶荼100%"},{"pid":"09e3768a4a69ad19b1e9753a88ea6ad4aef15fab","tid":843261,"uid":196077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T04:39:30.000Z","msg":"奶茶&gt;鴛鴦&gt;咖啡"},{"pid":"fa045250c5c6bc11601b790118b83de44a095a5a","tid":843261,"uid":53189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T04:48:04.000Z","msg":"奶茶十有九劣<br />\n大多數茶記d茶底都廢<br />\n無茶味得奶味<br />\n<br />\n咖啡就基本上好小會有劣<br />\n <br />\n咖啡&gt;鴛鴦&gt;奶茶"},{"pid":"b37d8c820e863f5d7cfe85ae132f593264600439","tid":843261,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T04:52:42.000Z","msg":"茶＞＞＞＞啡=鴦"},{"pid":"3f44ad059afb2219cd2610c65ab61148a52046cd","tid":843261,"uid":12000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T04:57:25.000Z","msg":"茶走&gt;齋啡&gt;鴛鴦"},{"pid":"5dc95c71bdbea75664de0736a2073461cdf0b455","tid":843261,"uid":203098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"有冇師兄試過三七鴛鴦？係唔係間間茶記都有？"},{"pid":"8b9c9cffaa89c02407bb503f05f5839031c79b36","tid":843261,"uid":151322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:16:54.000Z","msg":"茶走"},{"pid":"7457d7618bd5a87036333985c51d67db3bf7b381","tid":843261,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01